e going to prison. ++RTS mode, though a little basic, it's still lots of fun! ++Neutral:Soundtrack is pretty generic..?CONS:Ugh, Ship combat. ---Trade Grinding, though optional, can quickly make the game too easy. -Would've liked to have seen some voice acting, so I don't have to read walls of text each time I conduct trade, get missions, conduct research, etc. --Conclusion?8/10. One of my most favorite Space Sims.Space Rangers HD is a well-done Space Trading, pirating, researching, president running, planetary RTS, prison shanking, reaper menace filled game that is full of potential, and has been getting updates occassionally. (Hopefully this continues! I love the new updates Devs! Keep it up!)"
