 Positive (123 reviews)OVERALL: Very Positive (1,766 reviews)You don't need my review to tell you this game deserves its 15$.Best regards,Space Cadet Lyakusha Pyenchekryak-42.P.S.Do not look on my Steam in-game timer. I played it (SR1, SR2) years before release on Steam and I know what I'm talking about."
